        <item>
            <title>2.18.1</title>
            <pubDate>Sun, 26 Apr 2026 10:26:04 +0000</pubDate>
            <sparkle:version>2.18.1</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>2.18.1</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>13.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <sparkle:hardwareRequirements>arm64</sparkle:hardwareRequirements>
            <description><![CDATA[
                <ul>
                    <li>**#81**: Panel footer now refreshes the Sparkle last-check timestamp live via `UserDefaults.didChangeNotification` instead of only on panel open, keeping it in sync with the About screen</li>
                    <li>**#82**: When adding a raw timezone (e.g. America/Denver), the label now auto-defaults to the city component ("Denver") instead of empty string; works for multi-level IDs and UTC</li>
                    <li>**#84**: Added tooltip "Add a note to this timezone" to the ellipsis options button on each row; added "Drag to move the panel" to the float-mode drag handle so the UI is self-explanatory</li>
                    <li>**#86**: Added a Copy All button (doc.on.doc icon) to the panel footer — copies all timezone times at the current slider position as "6:15 PM Denver / 8:15 PM Chicago / ..." to the clipboard</li>
                </ul>
            ]]></description>
            <enclosure url="https://github.com/tpak/Meridian/releases/download/v2.18.1/Meridian.app.zip" length="3213524" type="application/octet-stream" sparkle:edSignature="DhUgjOwZKo0yST7mngiJOBViXVOLAu+U4w7uHZ/za5xbLXdQhwEntpLhY1EV69UMgd3Ol88t4pXuJDcD64j5DA=="/>
        </item>
